{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/add-name-field-to-debut-theme-newsletter","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1190,"date":"2021-10-08T01:50:07","date_gmt":"2021-10-08T01:50:07","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1190"},"modified":"2022-05-07T09:49:07","modified_gmt":"2022-05-07T09:49:07","slug":"add-name-field-to-debut-theme-newsletter","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/add-name-field-to-debut-theme-newsletter/","title":{"rendered":"Debut theme: how to add a &#8220;name&#8221; field to the newsletter"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>When it comes to reaching out to your target audience, keeping it <em>slightly</em> personal can be an interesting approach. Simply giving them the possibility to add their first name when asking for an email, will give you the possibility to send out emails with a more personalized feel to it and, potentially, boost up your conversions.<br><br>In this tutorial, I&#8217;ll show you how you can quickly and effortlessly add a &#8220;first name&#8221; field to your Debut theme&#8217;s newsletter: both section and the footer. You can <a href=\"https://debut-theme-slider.myshopify.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">click here</a> to view how the end result will look like. (Please scroll down to the footer).<br><br>Let&#8217;s do this!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-first\">Making a backup first</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-the-name-field-to-the-newsletter-section\">Adding the name field to the newsletter section</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Find&nbsp;the <strong>newsletter.liquid</strong> file.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"736\" height=\"593\" class=\"wp-image-1193\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></li><li>Press <strong>CTRL + F</strong> (or <strong>command + F</strong> on Mac) and search for exactly this (with quotes included):<br><br><em>type=&#8221;email&#8221;</em><br><br>You should find a line starting with <em>&lt;input</em>. In my case this is on the line 20, however, depending on your Debut&#8217;s version, this number can vary.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1169\" height=\"640\" class=\"wp-image-1195\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new2.jpg 1169w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new2-850x465.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new2-768x420.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1169px) 100vw, 1169px\" /><br></li><li>Now paste the following code <strong>above</strong> this line you found and save:<br><br>[gist]815ff3cb78f664307c322f0c937f4cc8[gist]<br><br></li><li>It should look like this:<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"867\" height=\"705\" class=\"wp-image-1197\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new3.jpg 867w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new3-850x691.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new3-768x624.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 867px) 100vw, 867px\" /><br><br></li><li>Great, we have successfully added the first name field to Debut&#8217;s newsletter section! Now let&#8217;s move on to the footer.<br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-the-name-field-to-the-footer-s-newsletter\">Adding the name field to the footer&#8217;s newsletter </h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Find the <strong>footer.liquid</strong> file.</li><li>Just like in the previous step, search for (with quotes included):<br><br><em>type=&#8221;email&#8221;</em><br><br>You will find the line starting with <strong>&lt;input</strong>. <br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1262\" height=\"662\" class=\"wp-image-1200\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new4.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new4.jpg 1262w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new4-850x446.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new4-1200x629.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/new4-768x403.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1262px) 100vw, 1262px\" /></li><li>Paste the code <strong>above</strong> the <strong>&lt;input</strong>  line and then save:<br><br>[gist]9586787d532a8b52d80b810a0ef671d0[gist]<br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-ok-but-where-do-i-view-the-customers-first-name-and-email-now\">Ok, but where do I view the customers&#8217; first name and email now?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>I&#8217;m glad you&#8217;ve asked! It&#8217;s actually quite simple. From your <strong>Shopify Admin</strong>, click on the &#8220;Customers&#8221; tab on the left side. In there you&#8217;ll be able to view all of your registered customers.<br><br>Once you click on one of them, then you&#8217;ll be able to view their email and other pertinent information.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1099\" height=\"454\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1210\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-3.png 1099w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-3-850x351.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-3-768x317.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1099px) 100vw, 1099px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"487\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-1-1200x487.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1206\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-1-1200x487.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-1-850x345.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-1-768x312.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/image-1.png 1207w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That is it, now you can capture your audience&#8217;s name and emails!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"custom-you-may-also-like\">Here are some other tutorials you may be interested in:<br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Add arrows &amp; swiping to Debut product pages<span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/3EkLfaQZ4YQKaZ26OY/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/debut-theme-product-page-images-zoom-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Debut &#8220;click to zoom&#8221; lightbox tutorial: mobile friendly images, slider &amp; arrows<span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/WR5Yl3hW8x6aUilwRe/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Improve your website&#8217;s safety: block right click, image copying and more</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><br></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Add an additional &#8220;name&#8221; field to your Debut theme&#8217;s newsletter.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1213,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[157],"acf":[],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/dawn_center-1-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/dawn_center-1-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/dawn_center-1-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["debut theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/dawn_center-1.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1190"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1190"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1190/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1658,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1190/revisions/1658"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/1213"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=1190"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embedd